.DT
do_chime
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
do_chime

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
do_chime -  This function is called by the chime handler.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void do_chime(string mess,
int type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^mess%^RESET%^ - the message set with set_chimes.
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of chime (quarter/half/hour)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/clock.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is called by the chime handler.
Overload this if you wish to have your own chime code.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_chimes

.EP

